data.description: Welcome to your new dream home! This inviting 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence is nestled in the coveted Pleasant Grove Independent School District, offering a serene and family-friendly atmosphere. With a delightful single living area, spacious breakfast and formal dining areas, and a host of other attractive features, this home is perfect for those seeking comfort and convenience.  Key Features: Generous Living Space: Step into the inviting single living area, perfect for cozy evenings and entertaining guests. The wood-burning fireplace adds warmth and charm, setting the stage for movie nights with loved ones. Dining Options: Enjoy meals with family and friends in both the breakfast area and the formal dining room, providing versatile spaces for every occasion. Bedrooms Upstairs: All three bedrooms are conveniently located upstairs, ensuring privacy and tranquility. Whether you're creating a nursery, home office, or personal retreat, you'll find the space you need. Wood Burning Fireplace: The wood-burning fireplace not only enhances the ambiance but also provides a cozy retreat during the cooler months. 2-Car Garage: A spacious 2-car garage offers ample storage space and protects your vehicles from the elements. Wet Bar Area: Entertain guests with style in the dedicated wet bar area, perfect for mixing cocktails and serving refreshments during gatherings. Fenced Backyard: The fenced backyard is an ideal setting for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply relaxing in your own  private oasis. This 2-story gem offers a harmonious blend of comfort and functionality.
